Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在风的节奏中推理渐渐清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的纠结也可以解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.13,0:00:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾危险的追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和琴酒与伏特加的对决究竟鹿死谁手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.38,0:01:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从被杀害的板仓先生的日记中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了与黑暗组织有关的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我和阿笠博士来到了板仓的别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.60,0:01:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 从伏特加那里打来了电话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你就在别墅里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.05,0:02:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回答我 板仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.81,0:02:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.42,0:02:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是抱歉 在黑暗中一时找不到电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.79,0:02:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就假扮板仓来引诱伏特加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约他在凌晨4点时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在施工中的贤桥车站的储物柜那见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.85,0:02:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上钩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在路上 博士的车子爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是只好拦下路过的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续向东京前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这两个人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.74,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗组织的接触（决死篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到了 两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去的贤桥车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那里不是还在施工吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在那里应该还没有电车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家就住在车站附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.99,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是便利呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 还可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新一 真的要去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.00,0:03:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.45,0:03:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前还有件事情得解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不知道你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过请不要在我车内讲悄悄话好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不是叫你不要抽烟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上丢掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.52,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不可以扔到窗外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丢到烟灰缸里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你把零钱和烟蒂放在一起不都脏了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你很有钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做是会遭报应的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这两个人就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝石抢匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆车的主人应该不是这位大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能是在山里丢弃做案用的赃车后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在半路上抢路过的人的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆车的主人是不抽烟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能方便付零钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把烟灰缸用来放零钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这位大哥哥没有注意到这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来他发现里面放了零钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是照样当作烟灰缸来用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我们上车之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了 弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些零钱是因为我讨厌他抽烟才故意放进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多证据证明这辆车不是大哥哥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不习惯在左边开车的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常不自觉的开到能够看清对面车子司机的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每当车子开到了马路中间时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面的车子不是经常鸣笛来表示抗议的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒车的时候也不由自主地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反复向视线不佳的左后方回头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.29,0:05:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他不习惯用右手来换档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有在转弯的时候没有打开方向灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而打开雨刷对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他忘记进口车和国产车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制杆的位置是左右相反的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我要上车的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明打开左边的门就可以让我上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你确要我从另一边上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来听了山村警官的一番话后 我终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为姐姐你坐的地方下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.58,0:06:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有另一个刚才腿部被抢击中的同伴所留下来的血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该就躲在后车箱里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了逃避路检 躲在那里避人耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么他们为什么还让我们上车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们当然不是因为好心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是一般的偷车贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会随便让人上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他们故意让我们上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了躲避路检
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为车子里要是载着老人和小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.00,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方就会以为我们是一家人而疏忽大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.93,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我已经发现这两个人的身份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不仅抢了别人的车又做出这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.96,0:07:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对就是正在逃亡的宝石抢匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 小弟弟你很聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.08,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么小就那么聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.77,0:07:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 既然被揭穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只好请你们跟我们一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.42,0:08:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是我们要在什么地方解决这老头和这小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.47,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这两个人想去的贤桥车站怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方什么人也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在天亮前施工人员也不会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在盘查的时候没有对警察说呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候你已经知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是宝石抢匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想浪费时间而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那里把你们交给警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同乘一辆车的我们就要去录口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就会耽误我很重要的约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你们两个我什么时候都可以抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 口气真硬啊 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 反正你说大话的时间也不长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时就算你哭着喊救命也不会饶了你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.81,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一时半会醒不过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了我的麻醉针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻醉针？什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.99,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这小鬼到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.06,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种宝石店店员认不出的模型枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骗不过我的眼睛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到底是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的是的 当心旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.03,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是随身足球腰带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特制的橡胶里充满气就变成足球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这种橡胶可以伸缩自如哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停充气的话还可以变得更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士给警察打个电话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说抓到了宝石抢匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你真要到交易地点去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里离贤桥车站还有一站路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这里来了警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙也不会停止交易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我担心的不是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事我会用侦探徽章联系你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前不要靠近贤桥车站啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看住车站的周围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.15,0:10:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一只老鼠也不准放过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 板仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.76,0:12:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板仓这混蛋竟然还没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支票？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.07,0:13:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和我们给板仓的金额不是一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.22,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是委托板仓制作的那个软件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.59,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 把钱留下还把东西也放在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.84,0:13:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是我 板仓应该还在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他抓到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.59,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.48,0:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进车站的只有醉汗和小孩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！再给我搜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.91,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴酒？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易应该是明天零点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.69,0:13:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙说明天不方便就改在现在这个时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:13:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.03,0:14:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是那家伙发电子邮件约定的时间？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是 时间是我们定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在原来的别墅收了邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说因为大雪停电了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就直接用电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没找到那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们要的软件到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙心脏不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.48,0:14:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们不杀他他迟早会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.13,0:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这个软件为什么会用胶带固定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.38,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了取得你的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.35,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为带着手套是撕不下胶带的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对方不出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会心神不安的点上香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要查查你的唾液就能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的血型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 连老巢都想要揪出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 盒子里有发报机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真是只狡猾的狐狸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板仓这个混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是板仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温差过大会刺激交感神经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加大心脏的附和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,患有心脏病的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.69,0:15:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会在暴风雪中跑到群马的别墅里去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.22,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么和我通电话的人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是那家伙雇的什么人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是出了岔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个盒子上的指纹虽然擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是盒子还是温的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.93,0:16:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还在这附近窥视着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来会被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 剩下的只有那里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.64,0:16:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾的狐狸现在变成笼中的老鼠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费话少说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.82,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.92,0:17:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 一个大人怎么会藏在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 大概是改装逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准已经叫了警察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.93,0:18:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你是说板仓雇的那个人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你要小心了 别再有下次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.14,0:18:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得有人注意组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.73,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是侦探一类的狐狸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？要不要去追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 还太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们假装逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们到底想要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让灰原制作奇怪的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又让板仓开发软件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象和药没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.05,0:19:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了人类而放弃的药物到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿笠博士 您的功劳真不小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然您已经累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还得麻烦您去录个口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 过来下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么呆会见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？千叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是犯人的伤势问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.97,0:19:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？脚步声？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.45,0:21:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人走过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…身体动弹不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？灰原？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.75,0:21:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.03,0:21:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你又为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.30,0:22:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和博士都没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用追踪眼镜找到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经早上了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.12,0:22:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹 找到你朋友了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.32,0:22:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快点出去吧 别妨碍我们施工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.53,0:22:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 工藤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.13,0:22:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来因为缺氧在箱子里失去知觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.97,0:22:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你到底在那里干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.22,0:22:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…因为好久没睡…就在那里打了个盹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这就是回答吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.35,0:22:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…应该算吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.85,0:22:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.54,0:22:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.88,0:23:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士他怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 博士应该和警察在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.98,0:23:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一条新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午5点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.29,0:23:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在米花大酒店发现一具男性尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.98,0:23:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是著名的CG设计师板仓卓 45岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.88,0:23:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.04,0:23:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.36,0:23:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.76,0:23:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.86,0:23:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黄莺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.70,0:23:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边就听得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.30,0:24:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是静山先生的鸟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.50,0:24:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.10,0:24:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话 那莫非…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.90,0:24:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.20,0:24:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳光普照的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.60,0:24:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄莺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.40,0:24:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月七日播出电影版 贝克街的亡灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影系列从四月十四日再续播哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.72,0:00:30.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海风中感觉到你的气息 银色的波浪消除了二人的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.73,0:00:43.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样让时间停止吧 远远看去藐小的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.29,0:00:53.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法再分离 与你约定在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:01:00.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在闪耀的季节中得来不易的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.09,0:01:08.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再迷惘 相信我的眼神 风的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.31,0:01:15.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在溢满的不安中隐藏泪水的昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.98,0:01:25.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的回忆现在终于可以说出 风的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.77,0:20:09.66,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到你的电话声 如此坚强的我也会哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.78,0:20:17.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管彼此伤害对方 但是还是想见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.17,0:20:22.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使结局终究令人厌恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.04,0:20:30.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对于给我的回答觉得为难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.93,0:20:38.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次回想起你那无法掩藏的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.01,0:20:42.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…I miss you
